  "remarks": "YEi.010. Designation: Major General, Houthi Commander of Yemen's Naval and Coastal Defense Forces. Houthi Naval Forces Chief of Staff, who has masterminded lethal attacks against international shipping in the Red Sea, plays a leading role in Houthi naval efforts that directly threaten the peace, security, and stability of Yemen. Physical Description: Eye Color: Brown; Hair: Brown.; Listing: Listed by the 2140 Committee on 26 September 2022",
